{"title":"Bedrock Sandals Releases New Cairn Evo C PRO Along With New Straps and Colors for 2026","link":"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-sandals-new-cairn-evo-c-pro-2026","date":1772634592000,"content":"<p><em>To celebrate 15 years of making best-selling adventure footwear, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/bedrock-sandals\" target=\"_blank\">Bedrock Sandals</a> is starting 2026 with some highly anticipated drops. New Evo C Cairn Pro sandals, sandal webbing colors, and Cascade Green Mountain Clogs.</em></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-5.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-5.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Bedrock Sandals’ 2026 product drop begins with the Cairn Evo C Pro Sandals, which combine their highest cushion footbed with pro-level features. The Evo C Pro is a true quiver-killer, with 20mm of EVA cushion between indestructible G-hook-and-heel straps and grippy Vibram® Megagrip soles. You’ll have to C it to believe it.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-1.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/03/2026_Bedrocks_Sandals-1.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Bedrock is also dropping three new sandal colorways across all models in 2026, Cascade Green, and Abstract Rock Pattern (In Navy and Brown), and releasing the Mountain Clog in Cascade Green.</p>\n<p>Get yours today over at <a href=\"https://bedrocksandals.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bedrock Sandals</a>!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-sandals-new-cairn-evo-c-pro-2026\">Bedrock Sandals Releases New Cairn Evo C PRO Along With New Straps and Colors for 2026</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ec91f475c9ca6ebb9cd89e0eae742fb977e566b871fbc55bcfbce93aa1273fee","category":"Cycling"}